# Alpaca Market Data — used by the trade execution chart (dev server only).
#
# Put secrets in EITHER:
#   - `.env`  (Vite default), or
#   - `keys.env` in the same folder as package.json (also supported).
#
# Restart `npm run dev` after saving. Quotes around values are optional.

ALPACA_API_KEY_ID=
ALPACA_API_SECRET_KEY=

# Optional — Massive (api.massive.com) stock aggregates for chart fallback when Alpaca ETH is empty or IEX-only.
MASSIVE_API_KEY=

# Production / GitHub Pages: origin of the Vercel chart proxy (folder vercel-chart-proxy). No trailing slash.
# Leave empty for local dev (Vite proxies /api/alpaca and /api/massive).
# VITE_CHART_API_ORIGIN=
